Class ApproxsimObjectFactory

java.lang.Object
  ApproxsimClient.object.ApproxsimObjectFactory

public class ApproxsimObjectFactory
extends Object

ApproxsimObjectFactory is mapping of different sources of ApproxsimObjects to instances of the same.

addEventListener

public static void addEventListener(FactoryListener listener)
Registers the listener for notifications on ApproxsimObject-creation. Note that the implementation of this event class is geared towards long-term listeners, for transient listening, consider reimplementing the listener list.

Parameters:
listener - listener to add
